                     <interp inst="t18150111-82-off465" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150111-82-off465" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18150111-82-cd466" type="crimeDate">19th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150111-82-off465 t18150111-82-cd466"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150111-82-off467 t18150111-82-cd466"></join>, twelve bushels of coals, value 1 l.
